"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-sport-peatys-mum-hopes-paris-olympics-will-be-his-last\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get the biggest sports news in your inbox  Britain's Adam Peaty is gunning for a third consecutive 100m breaststroke gold at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.308468500933595e-14, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703097123, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9355690384396339, \"rank\": 0.06884895685081838, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 249, \"end\": 259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: REUTERS  PublishedJul 16, 2024, 02:02 AM  UpdatedJul 16, 2024, 08:13 PM  LONDON-Adam Peaty may not have made up his mind, but his mother Caroline said on July 15 that she hopes the triple Olympic champion will give up competitive swimming after the Paris Games and live a more normal life.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 349, \"end\": 356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"REUTERS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 486, \"end\": 494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Records\", \"score\": 0.9592512096939689, \"rank\": 0.03856211459632521, \"text\": \"Caroline\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Records\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty, 29, is going for a third successive 100m breaststroke gold after becoming the first British swimmer to retain an Olympic title at the Tokyo Games in 2021.\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9798707372461892, \"rank\": 0.01790818843424531, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also has two Olympic relay silvers.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"American Michael Phelps is the only male swimmer to have won gold in the same event at three Games.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999806104119096, \"rank\": 1.82925128274263e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 851, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3906462737390044e-31, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty goes to Paris in July as an underdog, but at peace with himself and without pressure.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 956, \"end\": 961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999833705716, \"rank\": 1.6629344123325817e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world record holder reset his approach to the sport after overcoming issues with mental health and alcohol.\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He missed the 2022 world championships with a fractured foot and took time out in 2023.\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know that he's happy, he's in the place he wants to be now and he's more secure.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's ready as he will ever be,\\\" Caroline Peaty told BBC Radio.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1372, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.5188550011324827, \"rank\": 0.5173204141517794, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Knowing your child is suffering no matter how old they are is difficult.\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adam is very happy now - I think he's a better Adam personally than what he was before, the break has done him good.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's going into the Olympics not stressed, he's happy - what will be, will be.\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has an open mind on whether this is his last Olympics.\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hopefully want him to finish swimming and to have some kind of normality now.\\\"\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1794, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty, who has a three-year-old son, said in June that swimming had taken a toll on him.\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you achieve what I have in the sport, Olympic golds and world records, that comes at a cost,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I started (the current cycle) in a place where I had to take a break from the sport, a break from life really, because it's so demanding.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whatever the result is on the scoreboard, you want to look back on that experience with 'Wow, I gave it my best shot'.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would not ever regret giving it my best shot.\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am giving my best shot every single day.\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I would regret not even trying.\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could have stopped 14 months ago...\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd have been watching from afar, knowing that, at the back of my mind, I could have given it a shot.\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"REUTERS  Olympics  World record  Swimming  Olympics 2024  Mental health  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2587, \"end\": 2600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mental_health\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mental health\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mental_health\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mental_health\"}, {\"begin\": 2634, \"end\": 2642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RSS Feed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2751, \"entities\": []}]}"